        <mxCell id="note" value="No AC, no DC, no operator action, no external water needed for 72 h. Class 1E batteries (72 h) power MONITORING only. Standby diesels = defence-in-depth, not credited. SBO CDF ≈ 1e-11 /ry — 4 orders below the 1e-7 plant target; substantiates FER §8.8.3 'negligible SBO' claim." style="text;html=1;fontSize=10.5;fontColor=#55606a;align=left;spacing=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
